Package: blblm
Type: Package
Title: Linear/Logstic Regression with Bootstrap and parallelization
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jiahui Lu
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: This package help users to compute linear/logstic regression models and parameters 
    using Little Bag of Bootstraps technique. Users also have the option to use parallization
    while computing the fitted model. To use multiple CPU's, users will need to run 
    `suppressWarnings(plan(multiprocess, workers = 4))` and change number of workers to specify
    number of CPU's want to use.  
